trans-unit.source: Provides methods that ASP.NET uses to invoke the application-preload feature in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 提供 ASP.NET 用來叫用中的應用程式預先載入功能方法[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: Called by [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to notify ASP.NET whether an application should be preloaded.
trans-unit.target: 由呼叫[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]通知 ASP.NET 應用程式是否應該預先載入。

trans-unit.source: The unique ID of the application.
trans-unit.target: 應用程式的唯一識別碼。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to indicate that the application should be preloaded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>表示，就應該預先載入應用程式。否則， <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Calls [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to get information that is required in order to preload an application.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]取得預先載入應用程式所需的資訊。

trans-unit.source: IIS calls ASP.NET through this interface, supplying a reference to an object that implements the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil> interface.
trans-unit.target: IIS 會呼叫 ASP.NET 透過這個介面，提供物件，用於實作的參考<xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil>介面。</xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil>

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET uses that interface later to perform a callback into IIS to get preload information for individual applications.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 會使用該介面稍後執行回呼 iis 以取得個別應用程式預先載入的資訊。

trans-unit.source: The handle to an unmanaged interface in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that ASP.NET calls to get information.
trans-unit.target: Unmanaged 介面中的控制代碼[!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]該 ASP.NET 呼叫來取得資訊。
